2004;;Knots;;American;;Greg Lombardo;;Scott Cohen, Annabeth Gish, Paulina Porizkova;;comedy;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Knots_(film);;The film tells the story of a man (Scott Cohen) who discovers his wife (Annabeth Gish) is having an affair, and the consequences of their resulting relationship with the mistress (Paulina Porizkova).